{ With a clear advantage for Black. The only thing you have to remember is that the lesser evil for White is: }
11. Rxf2 Nxf2 12. Nxb7
{ although Black should be happy here as well with the extra exchange after both }
12... Rb8 { Or   12...Nh3+  ∓ } *

