20. Qc7
{ With the queen cut off White needs to watch out not to get mated-   20.Bb2 ?  Rxh4+  21.gxh4  Qxh4# }
20... Rde8 21. Bb2
{ Now Black can force a draw after exhausting all other possibilities with }
21... Rxh4+ 22. gxh4 Qxh4+ 23. Qh2 Bxg2+ 24. Kxg2 Qg4+ 25. Kh1 Qf3+ 26. Qg2
Qh5+ *

