{ Please note that the Taimanov move   8.Nge2  is best met with some useful semi-waiting move like  a6 !?  There is no need to free the White knights with   8...d5  9.Nxd5  Nxd5  10.cxd5  Qxd5  11.Nc3  although this might be also playable.  Or even   8...d6 !? }
8... Na5 9. Nf3 c6 10. Be2 d5
{ led to favourable central tension for Black, Miles,A  (2570)  - Ljubojevic,L  (2595)  Linares 1985 }
