{ In order to continue with d2-d3. But here we can use the fact that we are down a tempo and didn't play Ng8-f6 yet to go for active play }
5... Qf6
{ If you want calm equality, then   5...Nf6  6.Nc3  c6 =  followed by d7-d5 will do. }
